    <item>
      <title>流媒体收入下降，环球音乐收入下跌 30%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/universal-sinks-30-after-subscription-growth-misses-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[环球音乐集团 (Universal Music Group NV) 的订阅和流媒体收入增长令投资者失望，其股价一度下跌 30%，为该公司首次公开募股以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/universal-sinks-30-after-subscription-growth-misses-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:52:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国 CAC 40 指数较 5 月高点下跌 10%，有望回调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/france-s-cac-40-drops-10-from-may-high-set-to-enter-correction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受开云集团 (Kering SA) 等重量级企业业绩令人失望以及政治动荡令投资者对国家财政状况感到担忧的影响，法国股市即将从 5 月份的纪录高位回调 10%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/france-s-cac-40-drops-10-from-may-high-set-to-enter-correction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 07:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Stellantis 盈利几乎减半，引领汽车行业下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stellantis-earnings-plunged-in-first-half-on-weak-us-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[今年上半年，Stellantis NV 的盈利大幅下滑，令汽车行业前景愈发黯淡，此前该公司在美国和欧洲的销量大幅下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/stellantis-earnings-plunged-in-first-half-on-weak-us-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:30:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士宝盛集团股价下跌，因首席执行官职位空缺导致战略不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士宝盛集团有限公司 (Julius Baer Group Ltd.) 的股价周四成为欧洲主要银行中跌幅最大的一家，原因是利润大幅下降和对领导层空缺的担忧掩盖了收回客户资金的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/julius-baer-sees-client-inflows-accelerate-amid-benko-clean-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 05:22:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金属抛售加剧，铜价跌破 9,000 美元大关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/copper-sinks-below-9-000-threshold-as-metals-selloff-deepens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球股市下跌以及对中国等地区需求前景的悲观情绪加剧，铜价大幅下跌，自 4 月初以来首次跌破每吨 9,000 美元的关口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-25/copper-sinks-below-9-000-threshold-as-metals-selloff-deepens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 03:04:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
